/* KNOT-INJECT-CHAPTERS */

= My Document

Here is some text with an inline R expression: `{r} 1 + 1`.

```{r}
#| eval: true
#| echo: true
#| output: true

# Load libraries
library(ggplot2)

# Create some data
x <- 1:10
y <- x^2

# Display summary
summary(x)
```

The mean of `x` is `{r} mean(x)`.

```{r}
#| eval: true
#| echo: false
#| output: true

# Create a simple plot
df <- data.frame(x = x, y = y)
gg <- ggplot(df, aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point(size = 3, color = "steelblue") +
  geom_line(color = "steelblue", alpha = 0.5) +
  theme_minimal() +
  labs(
    title = "Simple Quadratic Function",
    x = "x",
    y = "y = x²"
  )

# Render the plot (requires knot.r.package)
typst(gg, width = 6, height = 4)
```
